column5: Monarchs are flying and the rain has come nuff said  Good Luck to all  Florescent Green J-13  Foam ear plug,recurve hook and a split shot  and a flourescent green and silver cleo what else is necessary...... oh yeah and a camera flash  Peter
i understand the other stuff but why the ear plugs?
I get really serious no matter what fish I'm targeting. But if it come down to me actually going out for salmon I wouldn't disagree with your selection a bit lol.
Just getting ready to get out. Got some cleos and some cyclops. Hopefully something is swimming out there.
